  "title": "Pirkei Avot §avot_04_10: Rabbi Meir said: Engage but little in business, and busy yourself with the To...",
  "body": "Rabbi Meir said: Engage but little in business, and busy yourself with the Torah. Be of humble spirit before all men. If you have neglected the Torah, you shall have many who bring you to neglect it, but if you have labored at the study of Torah, there is much reward to give unto you",
